        <para>27.
            <emph type="italic">Re-torque wheel/rim mounting nuts to specifications.</emph>
        </para>
        <seqlist>
            <item>
                <para>Determine nut size, type, and torque specification.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Re-torque all wheel rim nuts following the proper tightening sequence.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Refer to the Wheels, Rims, and Tires section in GROUP 17 in the Master Service Manual for
                    additional information.
                </para>
            </item>
        </seqlist>
        <figure id="f1000412" figsize="pg-wide">
