        <para>29.
            <emph type="italic">Tire air pressure. Fill to the proper inflation pressure.</emph>
        </para>
        <seqlist>
            <item>
                <para>Adjust tire pressure to maximum rating on the tire.</para>
            </item>
        </seqlist>
        <para>30.
            <emph type="italic">Front wheel hub and lift axle(s) oil level.</emph>
        </para>
        <seqlist>
            <item>
                <para>Inspect oil level through the hub cap window. The oil level should be between the oil level
                    indicators.
                </para>
            </item>
        </seqlist>
        <figure id="f1000411" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg10/G1000411.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="272px"/>
